{"tid":472585,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打玩過德州撲克？有冇興趣研究吓數學？","createTime":"2017-11-18T11:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T12:43:12.000Z","uid":123228,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c11e751d16e9f0264128e6da90a2ae15ad88e579","tid":472585,"uid":123228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係杜氏數學。<br />\n早幾個月初次接觸德州撲克，覺得好好玩，<br />\n得閒去HKPPA個Facebook睇吓佢啲直播。<br />\n咁我之前又拍過吓啲賭博數學嘅片，<br />\n所以就小試牛刀拍咗４條計德州撲克數學嘅片，<br />\n希望各位畀啲意見。<br />\n（內容偏淺，因為想先Target全無數學背景嘅觀眾先）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1h3Xw_uzaeY&amp;index=19&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1h3Xw_uzaeY%26index%3D19%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=94f8970f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1h3Xw_uzaeY&amp;index=19&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo</a><br />\n呢條簡介「Rule of Two」，點樣喺場上快速估算機率，同埋點解可以咁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E6MscUlx1vY&amp;index=20&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE6MscUlx1vY%26index%3D20%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=ee63dee6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E6MscUlx1vY&amp;index=20&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo</a><br />\n呢條計吓連續兩局拎Pair10嘅機率。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=saAKTv3XkZc&amp;index=21&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsaAKTv3XkZc%26index%3D21%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&d=OtBlgv7nJ%2FKEjpdHeujYZgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=787d6eb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=saAKTv3XkZc&amp;index=21&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au